Job Description 1 :

- Manage environments and configurations across DEV and QA streams for banking platforms.
- Environment preparation, refresh, rebuild, upkeep, maintenance, and upgrade activities.
- Troubleshooting and resolution of environment-specific issues, including infrastructure-related issues.
- Automation of regular/periodic environment-specific tasks through Jenkins.
- Develop and enhance scripts using Unix/Perl for requirements across market data sync.
- Automation of package deployments to UAT environments.

Skills:
Execution Sequencing, Dependency Mapping, Governance Structure Design, Initiative Tracking, Cross-Workstream Alignment, Operational Role Clarity, Delivery Visibility.

